posting_body: ['Welcome Home', 'The peaceful neighborhood of Linea sits along the waterline of the San Gabriel River within historic Georgetown.', "Explore the area's rich history and vibrant social scene by visiting one of its numerous dining and shopping spots.", 'Plus, Linea is minutes from both the I35 and SH 130, giving it small-town charm while being just a short drive to Austin and Round Rock.', 'Linea has five spacious varieties of three or four bedroom rental homes to choose from, all with two-car garages, open floor plans, tall ceilings, modern finishes, stainless steel appliances, private backyards and front porches.', "You can live in the home you've always wanted without the additional responsibilities and commitments.", 'We look forward to meeting you!', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 42', 'OR Text', '42', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our team directly.', 'Follow This Link for More Information:', '<URL>', 'This is a 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1266 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- 2-Inch Faux Wood Blinds', '- Wi-Fi Thermostats', '- Gas Ranges', '- Fully Landscaped Front Yards', '- Washer & Dryer Connections', '- Modern Cabinets with Cove Molding', '- Walk-In Closets', '- Private, Fenced Backyards with Grass & Irrigation', '- Vinyl Plank Flooring', '- GE Stainless Steel Appliances', '- Garage Door Openers', 'Community Amenities', '- Community Walking Trail', '- Along the San Gabriel River', '- Close to Wolf Ranch Town Center', '- Direct access to SH 130', '- Half Basketball Court', '- Pet Friendly', '- Park with Pavilion, BBQs & Pond', 'Pet Policy', 'Pet Friendly', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Saturday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Self Guided, after hours tours available!:', 'Linea Stillwater', '901 Big Rocky Bend, Georgetown , TX, 78626', 'Xmc6wnDTdFOE']
